{
  "//": "depcruise-only. Maps @opensip-tools/* to package SOURCE so dependency-cruiser resolves cross-package imports into packages/*/src (where the layer rules match). Without this, workspace imports resolve via each package's exports to dist/, which the cruiser's exclude + includeOnly drop — making every cross-package rule inert. NOT used for tsc builds; the real builds use each package's own tsconfig.",
